Nosipho Dumisa (amụrụ n'afọ 1988) bụ onye edemede South Africa, onye nduzi na onye na-emepụta ihe

O guzobere ụlọ ọrụ mmepụta ihe a na-akpọ Gambit Films. O dere ma duzie ihe nkiri mbụ ya, ihe nkiri mpụ na-akpali akpali Nommer 37, nke mbụ dị ka mkpirikpi na 2014 wee soro ya na 2018. O mepụtara usoro Netflix Blood & Water (2020). Ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka onye na-emepụta ihe nkiri na Afrikaans soap opera Suidooster
E gosipụtara ọrụ ya na South by Southwest
Ha emeriela ihe nrite mba ụwa. Ọ nọdụrụ na ndị ọka ikpe nke Neuchâtel International Fantastic Film Festival na Switzerland
Ọrụ ya na-egosipụtakarị Cape Town, ebe ọ bi, dị ka ọnọdụ.

Ọ bụ onye Zulu, mana ọ mụtara asụsụ Afrikaans n'ụlọ akwụkwọ. Na mbido ime ihe nkiri, njehie nchịkwa nke debanyere aha ya na usoro ihe nkiri kama ime ihe nkiri mere ka ọ chọpụta mmasị ya n'ihe na-eme n'azụ igwefoto. Ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ wee nweta nzere Bachelor of Arts na Motion Picture Medium site na AFDA na 2009.
